Four county schools -- San Clemente, Dana Hills, Trabuco Hills and Newport 
Harbor -- are entered in the San Dieguito tournament that begins Wednesday at 
three sites in north San Diego County. 
</P>
<P>
In the most interesting matchup of the first round, San Clemente and 6-7 center 
Eddie Morgan will open against perennial power Las Vegas Western. 
</P>
<P>
The championship game is scheduled for 7:30 p.m. Saturday. The first-round 
pairings: 
</P>
