<P>
Sidebar; Series 
</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
LOS ANGELES POLICE DEPARTMENT; POLICE -- LOS ANGELES; CRIME -- LOS ANGELES; 
BOMBINGS -- LOS ANGELES; LAW ENFORCEMENT; PLEA BARGAINING; SENTENCING 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
